WEBVTT

00:04:58.400 --> 00:05:00.840
more convenient and maybe even healthier.

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:05.480
But have we been lulled
into a false sense of security?

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:09.040
It starts simply by ticking a box.

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:11.656
Yes, we say,

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:13.120
I've read the terms.

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:18.280
But have you really read the terms?

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:21.496
Are you sure they didn't look too long

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:23.576
and your phone was running out of battery,

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:26.816
and the last time you tried
they were impossible to understand,

00:05:26.840 --> 00:05:28.680
and you needed to use the service now?

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:33.496
And now, the power
imbalance is established,